Hi ,can you pls review the campaign and get it approved asap

Hi Soniya, I understand that you want your campaign reviewed and approved as soon as possible. Unfortunately, I don't have the capability to expedite the approval process directly. However, you can ensure that your ad meets all the guidelines and requirements to avoid any delays. The ad approval process usually takes between 1-2 business days. If you have any specific concerns or need further assistance, please email our support team at adsupport@newsbreak.com.

Hi Soniya, it looks like you're referring to an ad campaign related to weight loss. Please note that ads promoting weight-loss products are subject to strict guidelines and may be rejected if they don't comply with our policies. If your ad was rejected, you might need to create a new ad that adheres to our policies from the start. For more details on what to do if your ad gets rejected, you can check out this article: [My ad got rejected - What's next?](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/18085960681101-My-ad-got-rejected-What-s-next). If you need further assistance, please email adsupport@newsbreak.com.
Hi there! How can I assist you today?
can you pls check why campaign is still showing payment method error however we have added funds yesterday

Sure, I can help with that. Could you please confirm if you have tried contacting your bank to resolve the payment matter or added a different payment method? If you have already done this and the issue persists, I recommend submitting a request to adsupport@newsbreak.com for further investigation. Please include details about the error and any relevant screenshots.
